Text:
HEY! I saw where you wanted to know where I got that 'absolutely orgasmic' Fall Out Boy Discography. Well, From Under The Cork Tree was a CD rip (Except for tracks 14-18), Folie A Deux was a CD rip from tracks 1-14, and both discs on Infinity On High were CD rips. Everything else I got from a few websites, corrected the info, and uploaded them here.


(Original quote from The Music Or The Misery on From Under The Cork Tree: I got your love letters, corrected the grammar, and sent them back.)
I'm sorry about that. My computer is not responding at all. But, happy uploading. If you ever need any more help, contact me.
